<bibRefCitation author="Vivallo, F." box="[399,566,2012,2038]" pageId="23" pageNumber="254" pagination="501 - 537" refId="ref23723" refString="Vivallo, F. (2013) Revision of the bee subgenus Centris (Wagenknechtia) Moure, 1950 (Hymenoptera: Apidae: Centridini). Zootaxa, 3683 (5), 501 - 537. https: // doi. org / 10.11646 / zootaxa. 3683.5.1" type="journal article" year="2013">Vivallo (2013)</bibRefCitation>
